headline.main: Eight-Year-Old Canadian Goalie's Dance Moves Go Viral
headline.print_headline: Eight-Year-Old Canadian Goalie's Dance Moves Go Viral

lead_paragraph: A barge breakaway at the Racine Lock and Dam on the Ohio River near Huntington, West Virginia, led to the closure of the waterway, the U.S. Coast Guard said on Thursday.
